messages.messageBody:
In a message dated 9/10/2003 1:26:03 PM Eastern Daylight Time,
UnschoolingDiscussion@yahoogroups.com writes:
A friend of mine who conducts orientation sessions for teens
traveling to Japan, asked me to post this scholarship notice for
homeschoolers.

Youth For Understanding USA
A high school flame's parents were directors for this group and I did some
volunteer work there, back in the day. They are a great opportunity.
Elissa
